title: What is this typeface?
content:
Hi guys,  
Someone could help me recognize this font? I tried in different ways but it’s to hard for me.  
It has a sort of Jenson’s spirit, but less precise, more close to Tribute (by emigre), Maxime, ecc...  
Thanks in advance
